# corpus (every vector + every //... rust_test target). This
# guard reads the manifest, the Core vector fixtures, the Phase 5 vectors, and
# every BUILD.bazel from DISK (via runfiles) and FAILS on any drift: a vector on
# disk missing from the manifest, a manifest entry with no vector, a stale
# (hardcoded-and-rotted) count, or a rust_test target added/removed without a
# manifest update. Counts are derived from reality, never trusted as written.
